cled materials – key unifi brands include sorbtek® reflexx® aio®  allinone performance yarns satura® augusta® amy® mynx® uv and microvista® unifis yarns are readily found in the products of major brands in the apparel hosiery automotive home furnishings industrial and other enduse markets to learn more about repreve® visit wwwreprevecomunifi is a global textile leader that will continue to benefit fromgrowing apparel production in the regions covered by the nafta  caftadrshifting global consumer preferences toward syntheticongoing enhancement of product portfolio through the growth of higher margin pva premium valueadded yarns driving higher margins and strong free cash flowsignificant international opportunities especially in asia and south america leveraging strong financial position and international sales and marketing capabilitiesunifi also employs a range of differentiating factors that provide for growth potential with defensibilitypva offeringsspecialty and technical yarnsinnovation and technologyvelocity to marketrange of volumediverse market segmentsunifi is the only company offering the entire spectrum of polymer to yarn to valueadded solutions in polyester and nylonfeatured content investor presentation  september   annual report q  earnings conference call transcript  q  unifi inc earnings conference call  presentation slides q  earnings conference call transcript  q  unifi inc earnings conference call  presentation slidesupcoming events more events  datetitleremind meprior to event  am etq  unifi inc earnings conference call days enter your email address  recent newsmore news unifi announces fourth quarter fiscal  earnings conference callgreensboro nc july   prnewswire  unifi inc nyse ufi will host a conference call at  am eastern time on wednesday july   to discuss its fourth quarter fiscal  financial results the fourth quarter fiscal  financial results and supporting materials will be available beginning the morning of the call on the companys websit